The paper discusses the benefits of using synthetic data for privacy and bias correction, which are common concerns in the field of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the use of synthetic data in machine learning (cs.LG) and data management (cs.DB) applications. Additionally, the paper touches on the ethical considerations of using real data, which is a topic of interest in the fields of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and cyber ethics (cs.CY).
